---
// No props — this section is editorial and rarely changes
---
<section class="summary" id="summary">
  <div class="summary-inner">
    <h2>What ETRI Library did with AI</h2>
    <div class="summary-callout">
      <p>
        ETRI Library used AI not as a standalone technology, but as a practical tool
        for service design, work automation, and library transformation.
      </p>
      <p>
        Across six cases — from building a custom kiosk to improving Google Scholar
        discoverability — the common thread is clear: AI lowered the barrier to
        solving real problems, without requiring a large IT team or major system
        replacement.
      </p>
      <p>
        The result is a library that moves faster, serves better, and thinks
        differently about what is possible.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .summary {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    padding: var(--space-8) var(--space-3);
  }

  .summary-inner {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .summary h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .summary-callout {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
    padding-left: var(--space-4);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .summary-callout p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
</style>
